# Make A Wish - Infinit Wish Board

I am currently Contributing to the Make A Wish, Infinite Wish Board Project.

It is a MERN Stack application and I am currently installing Helment.js for security. Helment.js is a framework that is meant to prevent code and command injection attacks, very important in the world we live in.
